description:
Elder Marcus Mason talks about the unprecedented times we are living in and also another pillar of our faith the Righteousness By Faith. Once we realize the times and who is the last generation some important questions for us to consider is how should we as Gods people be living in preparation to see Jesus in peace.

If the video will not play correctly please go to this link
https://www.apocalypseministries.org/aptv/
